Code.NativeIaC:
```bicep
resource server 'Microsoft.DBforMySQL/flexibleServers@2021-12-01-preview' = {
  name: '<example_resource_name>'
  location: '<example_location>'
  sku: { name: 'Standard_D2ds_v4', tier: 'GeneralPurpose' }
  properties: {
    highAvailability: {
      mode: 'ZoneRedundant' // Critical: enables zone-redundant HA
    }
  }
}
```

Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "azurerm_mysql_flexible_server" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name                = "<example_resource_name>"
  location            = "<example_resource_id>"
  resource_group_name = "<example_resource_id>"

  high_availability {
    mode = "ZoneRedundant"  # Critical: enables zone-redundant HA
  }

  administrator_login    = "adminuser"
  administrator_password = "<admin_password>"
  sku_name               = "GP_Standard_D2ds_v4"
}
```
